00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:34.060
we've made, why we've made them,
and what they mean to

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:36.410
you as an Android
app developer.

00:15:36.410 --> 00:15:38.670
So let's go ahead and step in
our time machine here, and

00:15:38.670 --> 00:15:40.030
we're going to roll all
the way back to

00:15:40.030 --> 00:15:41.630
Android 1.5, Cupcake.

00:15:41.630 --> 00:15:44.490
So for those of you who are
keeping score, this was

00:15:44.490 --> 00:15:48.120
