00:42:13.370 --> 00:42:17.460
reconfigure, because there's
such an interest in listening

00:42:17.460 --> 00:42:18.770
to Daria Musk perform.

00:42:18.770 --> 00:42:20.020
She went on for six hours.

00:42:20.020 --> 00:42:25.080
And from this small town girl
performing in New York's bars

00:42:25.080 --> 00:42:26.730
