01:38:04.390 --> 01:38:06.640
to allow you to be nimble focus
on your application.

01:38:06.640 --> 01:38:08.780
It's perfect for web apps,
games, and mobiles.

01:38:08.780 --> 01:38:10.590
So a great use case is, if
you're building any of these

01:38:10.590 --> 01:38:13.310
things, really take a look at
the cloud and App Engine.

01:38:13.310 --> 01:38:15.460
Focus on your application and
not the infrastructure.

01:38:15.460 --> 01:38:16.400
Don't worry about managing.

