There's all this data
being generated.

01:38:24.440 --> 01:38:25.370
Are your users happy?

01:38:25.370 --> 01:38:26.420
How can you take advantage
of this?

01:38:26.420 --> 01:38:28.360
How can you help make your
application better?

01:38:28.360 --> 01:38:31.000
And I think that's where all of
this massive amount of data

