You can use the same kind of web
stack you're normally used

01:39:49.320 --> 01:39:52.150
to, same tools on your
workstation, you're fine.

01:39:52.150 --> 01:39:53.710
Well, it's a hit.

01:39:53.710 --> 01:39:55.480
Now you're a mobile gamer, and
