01:41:14.420 --> 01:41:15.240
You don't know what it costs.

01:41:15.240 --> 01:41:17.040
It's hard to predict.

01:41:17.040 --> 01:41:18.820
And new expertise, new
employees, these are things

01:41:18.820 --> 01:41:20.230
that are hard to predict.

01:41:20.230 --> 01:41:23.150
So the total cost of
your scale-up,

01:41:23.150 --> 01:41:24.860
you don't know, right?

01:41:24.860 --> 01:41:28.180
And so when you don't know,
you're not in the application

01:41:28.180 --> 01:41:28.800
business anymore.

01:41:28.800 --> 01:41:30.260
You're in the infrastructure
business.

01:41:30.260 --> 01:41:31.600
And you're an application
developer.

01:41:31.600 --> 01:41:33.830
You're making a game, you're
making a crowd-sourced mobile

01:41:33.830 --> 01:41:35.280
app, something like that.

01:41:35.280 --> 01:41:37.540
So you don't want to be in the
infrastructure business.

