02:03:20.030 --> 02:03:22.110
Another similar one is
RequestAnimationFrame.

02:03:22.110 --> 02:03:26.060
Animation And
RequestAnimationFrame is a

02:03:26.060 --> 02:03:28.340
programmatic way of saying, I'm
going to be putting things

02:03:28.340 --> 02:03:31.340
out, I'm going to be drawing
things to the screen.

02:03:31.340 --> 02:03:34.450
