what's best as far as

02:03:34.450 --> 02:03:38.820
hardware, and so why don't you
take care how exactly to

02:03:38.820 --> 02:03:41.890
schedule this?

02:03:41.890 --> 02:03:46.470
So there's two good reasons
to use RAF,

02:03:46.470 --> 02:03:47.750
RequestAnimationFrame.

02:03:47.750 --> 02:03:49.810
So this is a blog post over
